==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ferraro
<hw>Fer*ra"ro</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>prop. n.</pos>
<def><person>Geraldine Anne Ferraro</person>, a United States
politician. Born in 1935, she was a congresswoman from New York in the
United States Congress from 1978 to 1984, and ran unsuccessfully in 1984
a candidate for Vice President of the United States, with <person>Walter
Mondale</person> as the Presidential candidate. She was the first woman
to be nominated by a major U. S. political party for the office of Vice
President.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

